txt.en: Defeat the fire drakes that have grown strong under the influence of Ghâshghurm. This will improve the safety of Talath Úrui.
Talath Úrui no longer suffers the ills of a large population of fire drakes thanks to your unyielding hand.
Fire drakes can be found in Talath Úrui, mainly near the Ghâshghurm.\n\nYou should defeat any fire drakes and their offspring that you encounter.
Defeated many fire drakes in Talath Úrui.
Fire drakes thrive in the embrace of the Ghâshghurm.
